The code you've posted doesn't allow the player to even take the candles, let alone put them in the lamp or take them out again  <!-- s:shock: --><img src="{SMILIES_PATH}/icon_eek.gif" alt=":shock:" title="Shocked" /><!-- s:shock: --> 

